    "data": [
        {
            "title": "傳特朗普以預錄方式在數字資產峰會講話 比特幣衝高後回落",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"傳特朗普以預錄方式在數字資產峰會講話 比特幣衝高後回落\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c25abf03f9e708ada369fc7e97c98455/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032016035258364.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">傳特朗普以預錄方式在數字資產峰會講話 比特幣衝高後回落</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據外媒引述消息報道，美國總統特朗普將於美東時間周四在紐約市舉行的數字資產峯會（DAS）上以預錄方式發表演講，並預期會公佈其後續加密貨幣政策。比特幣價格方面，今早曾衝高至87,453美元，其後回落及倒跌，暫報85,901美元。\n\n</p>\n<p>報道指出，特朗普今次演講將是美國歷史上首次有現任總統在加密貨幣行業會議上發表演講，會議還吸引了多位政界及行業領袖。\n\n</p>\n<p>本周早些時候，白宮總統數字資產顧問委員會執行主任Bo Hines在DAS發表講話，暗示政府希望為其最近宣佈的比特幣戰略儲備儲備比特幣。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059265/即時-財經-傳特朗普以預錄方式在數字資產峰會講話-比特幣衝高後回落",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-20 16:11:39",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黃竹坑道爆水管   水柱四樓高",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7c06e1046c41410a1072893dd87611ed/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032015573412159.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今（20日）午3時許，黃竹坑道1號近香港仔工業學校對開行人路爆水管，水柱直衝三、四層樓高，形成路邊噴泉，駛過車輛紛紛收慢，水務署正派人關閉水掣搶修。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148643/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃竹坑道爆水管，水柱四樓高。fb：陳榮恩\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ffbd079f5342bd5eb7802d5df1ebb99/2025-03/11_52.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃竹坑道爆水管，水柱四樓高。fb：陳榮恩\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148644/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃竹坑道爆水管，水柱四樓高。fb：陳榮恩\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/219904316e3d380d318ba0334a19b251/2025-03/12_45.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃竹坑道爆水管，水柱四樓高。fb：陳榮恩\n      </div>\n</div>