            "title": "車Cam直擊｜荃灣男子馬路踩「風火輪」 雙手插袋跌倒險捱車撞 網民嘲：型到盡頭就是⋯",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/5657517498d57c10b8178800c1ab8042/2025-03/FotoJet_9.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/c0b40262055c71f080035114c0db0102/3ae076eb932f48aba5505b7252d688a7-928292cb5accd18c4a68c8e6eb4e40f4-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dbc4303c899\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67dbc4303c89b\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fe0f0ca719d5dff78e99161ee6aa8d98/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032015274441229.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在馬路上違法使用電動可移動工具，隨時害己害人。今日（20日）網上流傳一段車Cam影片，顯示一名男子騎着「風火輪」在荃灣西樓角路的馬路上行駛，其間路上車流不絕，但事主雙手插袋旁若無人，狀甚「有型」。詎料畫面一轉，事主突然失平衡跌倒，頓變「滾地葫蘆」在馬路上翻滾。此時後方一輛復康巴士駛至，險將男子捲入車底，幸司機及時將車煞停，過程驚險。男子亦隨即爬起身，收拾「風火輪」離開。\n\n</p>\n<p>網民紛紛留言，直斥涉事男子「累人累物」，嘲諷對方：「冇辦法唔笑出聲」、「雙手插袋實在太有型⋯⋯」、「型到盡頭就是⋯⋯」、「又要型又要威又要害人」。亦有網民稱：「都係個句，應該要規範左（咗）佢（電動可移動工具）。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148424/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1fa5d908c49bfb98eced5965e0627377/2025-03/0_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148425/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/944c3ab0d5a5306a287f8ad18648602f/2025-03/1_33.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148426/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2efb3e7e6df6a3ef694a5534f46df8c1/2025-03/2_0_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb車cam L（香港群組）影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4148427/t