            "title": "NBA｜當積大爆發破湖人隊史紀錄 領軍輕取金塊重上第3",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"當積單節已入21分。Getty\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/46d7522bb9c13659e4ddd7472567b1b6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250320/_2025032014590018663.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">當積單節已入21分。Getty</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周三NBA，湖人球星當積(Luka Doncic)大爆發首節已轟入21分，最終全場收穫31分，個人同時創下兩項隊史紀錄，領軍主場以120:108輕取殘陣的金塊，賽後壓過對方升上西岸第3位，當積賽後喜言愈來愈適應這支新東家了。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積全場入31分。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68f4298c3842132cb068992b901c25ff/2025-03/GettyImages-2205962429.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積全場入31分。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積全場入31分。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fe53dbf3ae698578ba080c572fcf414d/2025-03/GettyImages-2205971981.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積全場入31分。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積全場入31分。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62bd943da87f1b04988c9ed2a1935f24/2025-03/GettyImages-2205972295.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積全場入31分。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積全場入31分。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dfa8d443dd8716e0a12b9c29cb8fd7ed/2025-03/GettyImages-2205972187.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積全場入31分。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"湖人輕取金塊。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8694ee31b77af3bc0b727fd2e9ae90d1/2025-03/GettyImages-2205972240.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        湖人輕取金塊。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"湖人輕取金塊。Getty\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f92ed0d4618ef68fdec0bd4674e5a702/2025-03/GettyImages-2205971658.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        湖人輕取金塊。Getty\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>當積大爆發破紀錄</h2>\n<p>在勒邦占士繼續養傷下，湖人由當積擔任領軍人物。此子今場極速入局，第一節已經11次起手7中轟入21分，同時取得籃板和助攻各3次，以及偷波和封阻各1次，成為紫金軍隊史首位可單節錄得此數據的球員。最終，他只打3節下取得31分，領軍輕取有約基治和占姆梅利皆缺陣的金塊。而他今場射入4個三分球，也成為隊史最快入50個三分球的球員。\n\n</p><h2>「愈來愈適應」</h2>\n<p>當積被交易至湖人後，至今上陣16場場均貢獻26.5分和8.8.個籃板，表現漸回復水準，他賽後也喜言：「來到湖人後感覺就像搬進了一個新家。來到這裏，我努力建立新的家園，並也愈來愈適應了。尤其當我命中一些瘋狂的投籃時，我能感覺到球迷們的能量。不僅為我，也是為全隊注入能量。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
